[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 283     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m     # financial data almost always is). A patient with no payment history
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 284     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m     # gets placed in the middle of the distribution rather than at an extreme.
