[0m[49m[39m  301, 269[0m:[39m[49m ## Step 3: Run Clustering and Evaluate
[0m[49m[39m  302, 270[0m:[39m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;9m- 303     [0m:[38;5;9m[49m *The pseudocode calls this `cluster_patients(feature_matrix, k_range)`. It runs K-Means for each candidate k, computes silhouette scores, and returns the best model along with all results for comparison.*
